OL,3,CKen Reid receives QUB medal for
OL,4,Cservices to journalism
OL,6,FUTV's former political editor Ken Reid
OL,7,Fhas been honoured by Queen's
OL,8,FUniversity Belfast for services to
OL,9,Fjournalism.
OL,11,FKen was presented with a QUB
OL,12,FChancellor's Medal during a special
OL,13,Fceremony on Thursday evening.
OL,15,FAlso receiving the award was Stephen
OL,16,FGrimason, the BBC journalist who broke
OL,17,Fthe story of the signing of the Good
OL,18,FFriday Agreement in 1998.
OL,20,FKen said: "I'm very humbled, it's
OL,21,Freally an honour that was unexpected.
