OL,3,CKen Reid receives QUB medal for
OL,4,Cservices to journalism
OL,6,F"I think more than it's for me, it's
OL,7,Ffor everybody at UTV who helped me
OL,8,Fthrough all those great stories and
OL,9,Ftimes and really historic moments.
OL,11,F"I'm delighted that Queen's University
OL,12,Fare giving this honour not only to
OL,13,Fmyself but to my great friend - and
OL,14,Frival in many ways - Stephen Grimason."
OL,16,FKen Reid joined UTV in 1994 and led
OL,17,Fthe channel's coverage of politics for
OL,18,Fseveral decades, reporting on some of
OL,19,Fthe biggest moments in Northern
OL,20,FIreland's history.
