OL,3,CKen Reid receives QUB medal for
OL,4,Cservices to journalism
OL,6,FHe stepped down from the role of
OL,7,Fpolitical editor in 2021, but is still
OL,8,Fa regular contributor on View From
OL,9,FStormont and political programming on
OL,10,Fthe BBC.
OL,12,FThe Belfast-born journalist started
OL,13,Fhis professional career with The News
OL,14,FLetter newspaper, where he worked
OL,15,Fthere for seven years from 1977.
OL,17,FHe later worked with the Sunday News,
OL,18,Fwhere he became editor, and the Cork
OL,19,FExaminer.
