OL,3,CKen Reid receives QUB medal for
OL,4,Cservices to journalism
OL,6,FKen was named News Broadcaster of the
OL,7,FYear twice at the CIPR Press and
OL,8,FBroadcast Awards in 2005 and 2006.
OL,10,FThe Queen's University Chancellor's
OL,11,FMedal Awards were inaugurated last
OL,12,Fyear during a conference which marked
OL,13,Fthe 25th anniversary of the signing of
OL,14,Fthe Good Friday Agreement.
OL,16,FThe university says the awards were
OL,17,Fcreated to celebrate achievement in
OL,18,Fcivic leadership in all its aspects.
